{"tid":491923,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"Assassin’s Creed Black Flag 官方限時免費","createTime":"2017-12-07T04:11:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-13T15:32:05.000Z","uid":82279,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"dad56edaee18277a532063a3d21cd4385f438c0c","tid":491923,"uid":82279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T04:11:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://blog.ubi.com/get-two-ubisoft-pc-classics-free-december/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fblog.ubi.com%2Fget-two-ubisoft-pc-classics-free-december%2F&d=tQLHp1GlwDP%2BhlMP508MGKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=80933c55\" target=\"_blank\">http://blog.ubi.com/get-two-ubisoft-pc-classics-free-december/</a><br />\n<br />\n嚟緊12月Ubisoft 有兩隻驚限時免費，有興趣嘅記得睇時間上佢網站用uplay 下載。<br />\n<br />\n1. <strong>12月4日至12月11日</strong> 衝突世界 World in Conflict 連 Soviet Assault DLC (2007)<br />\nMeta critic 89分<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.metacritic.com/game/pc/world-in-conflict\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metacritic.com%2Fgame%2Fpc%2Fworld-in-conflict&d=tQLHp1GlwDP%2BhlMP508MGKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=e87a4570\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.metacritic.com/game/pc/world-in-conflict</a><br />\n<br />\n2. <strong>12月12日至12月18日</strong> 刺客教條：黑旗Assassin&rsquo;s Creed Black Flag（2013）<br />\nMeta critic 83分<br />\n <a href=\"http://www.metacritic.com/game/playstation-4/assassins-creed-iv-black-flag\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metacritic.com%2Fgame%2Fplaystation-4%2Fassassins-creed-iv-black-flag&d=tQLHp1GlwDP%2BhlMP508MGKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=7af38e19\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.metacritic.com/game/playstation-4/assassins-creed-iv-black-flag</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">攞咗一次就可以永久免費玩，唔係試玩版嚟</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nfrom December 4 (9AM PST) through on December 11 (2AM PST), you&rsquo;ll be able to download World in Conflict and its expansion (Soviet Assault) for free. Then, in honor of the tenth anniversary of the first Assassin&rsquo;s Creed game, you&rsquo;ll be able to get Assassin&rsquo;s Creed IV Black Flag for free from December 12 (6AM PST) through December 18 (2AM PST). As long as you download the games through Uplay during their free periods, they will be yours to keep and play whenever you like."},{"pid":"e1c8b35297883f58559d88f92037b143b42461f2","tid":491923,"uid":51670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T04:13:08.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"24f60cbf712fbb46c16ddcb2a585691087c1a8c0","tid":491923,"uid":27483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T04:16:41.000Z","msg":"Lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2552cf878dd267a066b4613fee92bce6735047ff","tid":491923,"uid":33357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T04:21:39.000Z","msg":"留名dl"},{"pid":"bf5c7c0ebaf21ceec86c651f2ced13f66d995e15","tid":491923,"uid":123764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T08:12:16.000Z","msg":"ps4？"},{"pid":"750ce75f42728a7376ab291e9f7ece3c6363788f","tid":491923,"uid":1039,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T08:15:22.000Z","msg":"有誠意嘅就出unity啦仲black flag<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71ae6f8a9ff82b24627bce1d3f8601b1b923475c","tid":491923,"uid":48222,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T08:36:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有誠意嘅就出unity啦仲black flag<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不了"},{"pid":"f234d91b3fe1e200a7dc2eb354a2b77aefe5343f","tid":491923,"uid":36148,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T08:37:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有誠意嘅就出unity啦仲black flag<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nUnity 差過 Black Flag好多......"},{"pid":"1763e7097e8bc51df037964d3b86e56601b2a2d0","ti